track_notes: Park on the side of the road, as indicated by the start of the Track on the map. Walk west along the road, until you come to an obvious trail. It is between some metal posts, on the right. Follow the trail. Turn right, off the trail, and bushwhack to the summit. Shorter than taking the trail, all the way up, but more difficult.

Park on the side of the road, as indicated by the start of the Track on the map. Walk west along the road, until you come to an obvious trail. It is between some metal posts, on the right. Follow the trail. There are a number of choices, along the way, but you will get to the summit eventually. Longer than bushwhacking, but easier.
